title: Tina Fey As Sarah Palin In VP Debate On SNL (VIDEO)

Tina Fey As Sarah Palin In VP Debate On SNL (VIDEO)

4th October 2008

Saturday Night Live's sketch about the vice presidential debate starred Queen 

Latifah as debate moderator Gwen Ifill, as well as Tina Fey, reprising her role as 

Governor Sarah Palin.
